Money Stuff =0A Programming note! I am not completely sure, but my best evi=
dence is that the =0Afirst edition of Money Stuff, in the form of an email =
newslette =0A=0A=0A <> =0A =0A<https://sli.bloomberg.com/click=3Fs=3D825881=
&stpe=3Ddefault&li=3D12513767&m=3D21d6dea82d6b16615cf44233be620525&p=3D0204=
2025>=0A=0A=0A=0AHappy birthday to me=0A=0AProgramming note! I am not compl=
etely sure, but my best evidence is that the =0Afirst edition of Money Stuf=
f, in the form of an email newsletter with that =0Atitle, was published10 y=
ears ago today <>. If you had asked me then if I would =0Astill be writing =
this email newsletter a decade later, I would have said =E2=80=9Chuh, =0Ath=
at would be cool.=E2=80=9D It has been! It has been an absurd privilege to =
get to =0Awrite Money Stuff, I look forward to doing it for many more years=
, and I am =0Aintensely grateful to you, my readers, for making it possible=
.=0A=0A=0ASports betting in your brokerage app=0A=0AI guess this was inevi=
